# 📚 Books Bazaar

Books Bazaar is a full-stack web application that allows users to:
- 🛒 Buy new books
- 🔁 Buy/sell used books
- ✏️ Shop for stationery items

This project includes user authentication, cart management, product filters, search functionality, and a responsive UI.

---

## 🔧 Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Backend**: Spring Boot (Java)
- **Database**: SQL (MySQL/PostgreSQL compatible)

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 Login/Logout support
- 🛒 Add to Cart / Buy Now functionality
- 🔍 Unified search across all categories
- 🎯 Filters by category, price, and rating
- 🖼️ Product cards and cart sidebar UI
- 🌐 Responsive design for all devices

